    request.

    No functional changes.

0.003		2022-09-30	T. R. Wyant
    Localize $_ before while (<>) reading config file in
    Date::ManipX::Almanac::Date.

    Add CONTRIBUTING.

0.002		2021-08-09	T. R. Wyant
    In English, add 'up' and 'down' as synonyms for 'rise' and 'set'.

    English did not parse twilight types at the beginning of twilight.
    That is "end of astronomical twilight" was parsed, but "beginning of
    astronomical twilight" was not. Fixed.

    In English, Allow (but ignore) "when" before bodies, as in "tomorrow
    when the sun rises"

0.001		2021-07-13	T. R. Wyant
    Initial production release.
